metadata.description:
First piece of art on blockchain under Marko Zubak contract. This work was made in occasion of CryptoVoxel Art Tour and Cent Art Network. Anonymous Regulator is a papertoy made in collaboration with Mattia Cuttini and tokenized on KnownOrigin (https://dapp.knownorigin.io/edition/68875). MLIBTY Shadows is one of the artist's biggest series and more about it available here: https://www.patreon.com/mlibty.

This contract was created to experiment with other approaches in artist's digital production. Below you can find links to other platforms with his work.

Edition: 1 of 1 | Exclusive Art on Blockchain | http://markozubak.com/ | https://superrare.co/MLIBTY | KnownOrigin: https://bit.ly/2N70h3S | https://opensea.io/assets/cryptoskateboards
